<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The Antidrug Club at Haramaya University is a student-led initiative dedicated to creating a drug-free society. We believe that every student has the potential to lead a fulfilling life without the influence of harmful substances like Chat, Alcohol, and Tobacco.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Founded in 2024, our club has grown from a small group of concerned students to a university-wide movement. We organize workshops, awareness campaigns, and recreational activities to promote a healthy lifestyle and provide a supportive community for all students.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
                To be a leading force in drug prevention and youth empowerment within Haramaya University and the surrounding community.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700">
                <li>Raise awareness about the dangers of substance abuse.</li>
                <li>Provide peer support and counseling resources.</li>
                <li>Organize drug-free social events.</li>
                <li>Advocate for university policies that support student well-being.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-6 text-center">Message from the President</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/4 mb-4 md:mb-0 text-center">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500">
                    <i class="fas fa-user text-4xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mt-2">Husica</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Club President</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-3/4 md:pl-8">
                <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
                    "Welcome to the Antidrug Club! As students, we face many pressures, but turning to drugs is never the answer. Our club is here to show you that you can have fun, succeed academically, and build a great future without substance abuse. Join us in making Haramaya University a healthier place for everyone."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
